    "english": "Tradin' sugar cane and rum and all the things he can't afford",
    "ipa": "/trædɪn ʃʊɡɚ keɪn ænd rʌm ænd ɔl ðə θɪŋz hi kænt əfɔrd/",
    "chinese_translation": "打理着他付不起的甘蔗和朗姆酒的买卖来谋生",
