    "song_id": "01-alexander-hamilton",
    "line_index": "44",
    "english": "Plannin' for the future see him now as he stands on",
    "ipa": "/plænɪn fɔr ðə fjutʃɚ si hɪm naʊ æz hi stændz ɔn/",
    "chinese_translation": "憧憬着未来，现在他终于站上",
    "note": "",
