    "song_id": "03-my-shot",
    "line_index": "75",
    "english": "What are the odds the gods would put us all in one spot",
    "ipa": "/wʌt ɑr ðə ɑdz ðə ɡɑdz wʊd pʊt ʌs ɔl ɪn wʌn spɑt/",
