    "song_id": "05-the-schuyler-sisters",
    "line_index": "56",
    "english": "You want a revolution? I want a revelation",
    "ipa": "/ju wɔnt ə rɛvəluʃən aɪ wɔnt ə rɛvɪleɪʃən/",
    "chinese_translation": "你希望爆发革命？我想将真相阐明",
