    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "05-the-schuyler-sisters",
    "line_index": "58",
    "english": "\"We hold these truths to be self-evident That all men are created equal\"",
    "ipa": "/wi hoʊld ðiz truθs tə bi sɛlfɛvɪdənt ðæt ɔl mɛn ɑr krieɪtɪd ikwəl/",
    "chinese_translation": "“我们相信所有公民生而平等是真理不证自明”",
