    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "10-helpless",
    "line_index": "83",
    "english": "But I'll never forget my mother's face, that was real",
    "ipa": "/bʌt aɪl nɛvɚ fɚɡɛt maɪ mʌðɚz feɪs ðæt wʌz riəl/",
    "chinese_translation": "我从未忘记我母亲真切的脸，",
    "note": "",
