    "song_order": "13",
    "song_title": "Wait for It",
    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "13-wait-for-it",
    "line_index": "75",
    "english": "He seems to thrive when so few survive, then Goddamnit—",
    "ipa": "/hi simz tə θraɪv wɛn soʊ fju sɚvaɪv ðɛn ɡɑdəmnɪt/",
    "chinese_translation": "众人败下阵来，唯独他乘胜追击——天煞也！",
