    "song_id": "24-what-d-i-miss",
    "line_index": "18",
    "english": "Thomas Jefferson's coming home!",
    "ipa": "/tɑməs dʒɛfɚsənz kʌmɪŋ hoʊm/",
    "chinese_translation": "托马斯·杰斐逊回家了！",
