    "song_id": "24-what-d-i-miss",
    "line_index": "22",
    "english": "Thomas Jefferson's coming home. Lord he's",
    "ipa": "/tɑməs dʒɛfɚsənz kʌmɪŋ hoʊm lɔrd hiz/",
    "chinese_translation": "托马斯·杰斐逊回家了！上帝啊他真是",
