    "song_id": "28-the-room-where-it-happens",
    "line_index": "89",
    "english": "No one else was in the room where it happened",
    "ipa": "/noʊ wʌn ɛls wʌz ɪn ðə rum wɛr ɪt hæpənd/",
    "chinese_translation": "再无他人置身这决策的现场",
