    "song_title_zh": "",
    "song_id": "28-the-room-where-it-happens",
    "line_index": "116",
    "english": "If you stand for nothing, Burr, what do you fall for? (What do you want Burr, what do you want?)",
    "ipa": "/ɪf ju stænd fɔr nʌθɪŋ bɝ wʌt du ju fɔl fɔr wʌt du ju wɔnt bɝ wʌt du ju wɔnt/",
