    "song_id": "46-who-lives-who-dies-who-tells-your-story",
    "line_index": "69",
    "english": "In their eyes I see you, Alexander",
    "ipa": "/ɪn ðɛr aɪz aɪ si ju ælɪɡzændɚ/",
    "chinese_translation": "而你仿佛在他们的眼中游荡",
