    "song_id": "46-who-lives-who-dies-who-tells-your-story",
    "line_index": "75",
    "english": "Oh, I can't wait to see you again",
    "ipa": "/oʊ aɪ kænt weɪt tə si ju əɡɛn/",
    "chinese_translation": "我已等不及与你当面互诉衷肠",
